<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{أَفَرَأَيْتُمُ النَّارَ الَّتِي تُورُونَ , أَأَنْتُمْ أَنْشَأتُمْ شَجَرَتَهَا أَمْ نَحْنُ الْمُنْشِئُونَ نَحْنُ جَعَلْنَاهَا تَذْكِرَةً وَمَتَاعًا لِلْمُقْوِينَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٢٠:</span> <span class="c3">{تُورُونَ}</span>: تَسْتَخْرِجُونَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">أَوْرَيْتُ:</span> أَوْقَدْتُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{لِلْمُقْوِينَ}</span>: لِلْمُسَافِرِينَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَالقِيُّ:</span> القَفْرُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الواقعة: ٧١ - ٧٣]</p> </div>